Manta Glide				KEY:SIMIC HYBRID ~ Animal Enhancement ~ Manta Glide					SORTKEY:1_Race	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.SIMIC HYBRID Race Trait.SIMIC HYBRID Animal Enhancement.SpecialQuality		DESC: You have ray-like fins that you can use as wings to slow your fall or allow you to glide. When you fall and aren't incapacitated, you can subtract up to 100 feet from the fall when calculating falling damage, and you can move up to 2 feet horizontally for every 1 foot you descend.
Nimble Climber			KEY:SIMIC HYBRID ~ Animal Enhancement ~ Nimble Climber				SORTKEY:1_Race	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.SIMIC HYBRID Race Trait.SIMIC HYBRID Animal Enhancement.SpecialQuality		DESC: You have a climbing speed equal to your walking speed.
Underwater Adaptation		KEY:SIMIC HYBRID ~ Animal Enhancement ~ Underwater Adaptation			SORTKEY:1_Race	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.SIMIC HYBRID Race Trait.SIMIC HYBRID Animal Enhancement.SpecialQuality		DESC: You can breathe air and water, and you have a swimming speed equal to your walking speed.
Grappling Appendages		KEY:SIMIC HYBRID ~ Animal Enhancement ~ Grappling Appendages			SORTKEY:1_Race	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.SIMIC HYBRID Race Trait.SIMIC HYBRID Animal Enhancement.SpecialQuality	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=5	DESC: You have two special appendages growing alongside your arms. Choose whether they're both claws or tentacles. As an action, you can use one of them to try to grapple a creature. Each one is also a natural weapon, which you can use to make an unarmed strike. If you hit with it, the target takes bludgeoning damage equal to ld6 +your Strength modifier, instead of the bludgeoning damage normal for an unarmed strike. Immediately after hitting, you can try to grapple the target as a bonus action. These appendages can't precisely manipulate anything and can't wield weapons, magic items. or other specialized equipment.
Carap ace				KEY:SIMIC HYBRID ~ Animal Enhancement ~ Carap ace					SORTKEY:1_Race	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.SIMIC HYBRID Race Trait.SIMIC HYBRID Animal Enhancement.SpecialQuality	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=5	DESC: Your skin in places is covered by a thick shell. You gain a +1 bonus to AC when you're not wearing heavy armor.
Acid Spit				KEY:SIMIC HYBRID ~ Animal Enhancement ~ Acid Spit					SORTKEY:1_Race	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.SIMIC HYBRID Race Trait.SIMIC HYBRID Animal Enhancement.SpecialQuality	PREPCLEVEL:MIN=5	DESC: As an action, you can spray acid from glands in your mouth, targeting one creature or object you can see within 30 feet of you. The target takes 2d10 acid damage unless it succeeds on a Dexterity saving throw against a DC equal to 8 +your Constitution modifier+ your proficiency bonus. This damage increases by ldlO when you reach 11th level (3dl0) and 17th level (4d10). You can use this trait a number of times equal to your Consitution modifier (minimum of once), and you regain all expended uses of it when you finish a long rest.



